msgid ""
"To view, manage, and create boot environments using the |sysadm| graphical "
"client, go to :menuselection:`System Management --> Boot Environment "
"Manager`. In the example shown in :numref:`Figure %s <be1>`, there is an "
"entry named *initial* that represents the original |trueos| installation."
msgstr ""

