msgid "Each entry contains the same information:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../sysadmclient.rst:560
msgid ""
"**Name:** The name of the boot entry as it will appear in the boot menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../sysadmclient.rst:563
msgid ""
"**Nickname:** A description, which can be different from the "
