"replication. Available choices are :guilabel:`Sync with snapshot` (at the "
"same time a snapshot is created), :guilabel:`Daily` (when selected, displays"
" a time drop-down menu so you can select the time of day), "
":guilabel:`Hourly`, every :guilabel:`30 minutes`, every :guilabel:`10 "
