"select the :guilabel:`Frequency`. Supported frequencies are \"Daily\", "
"\"Weekly\", or \"Monthly\". If you select \"Daily\", you can configure the "
"\"Hour\". If you select \"Weekly\", you can configure the \"Day of week\" "
"and the \"Hour\".  If you select \"Monthly\", you can configure the \"Date\""
" and \"Hour\". Since a scrub can be disk I/O intensive, it is recommended to"
" pick a time when the system will not be in heavy use."
